Detailed Description

cvmx_pci_cfg04

PCI_CFG04 = Fifth 32-bits of PCI config space (Base Address Register 0 - Low)

Description: BAR0: 4KB 64-bit Prefetchable Memory Space [0]: 0 (Memory Space) [2:1]: 2 (64bit memory decoder) [3]: 1 (Prefetchable) [11:4]: RAZ (to imply 4KB space) [31:12]: RW (User may define base address)
